name: PS-16. MetaBall-Pseudorandom
description:
v4W.ENko - "PS-16. MetaBall-PseudoRandom". The basic "PseudoRandom" is generating 67 vertices to continue the visual story about the "MetaBall Algorithm". The 31 outlines are colored in the list of 67 complementary colors depended on the sub-settings of the "metaball" charge centers.  "Pattern Standardization" series is upgraded with more complicated "MetaBall" structure and generating the form such as the "Abstract michro-scheme".
Packed as GIF. 1024*1024px / 180 frames.
